    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自行车公园模拟器是一款逼真的BMX、越野跳跃和山地自行车模拟游戏，让您体验自由骑行的乐趣。您可以选择三种不同类型的自行车，探索一个为所有技能水平的骑行者设计的大型沙盒滑板公园。凭借有趣的物理控制，玩家可以执行特技、抓住大气，并驾驭各种挑战性地形。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274780/extras/5405288a63244b1ba5a07e993ac1e7b2.avif?t=1772360936\" width=600 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274780/extras/03e1d5921cd25e412ee84235f1d01d00.poster.avif?t=1772360936\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274780/extras/03e1d5921cd25e412ee84235f1d01d00.webm?t=1772360936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274780/extras/03e1d5921cd25e412ee84235f1d01d00.mp4?t=1772360936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于自行车公园模拟器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自行车公园模拟器是一款逼真的BMX、越野跳跃和山地自行车模拟游戏，让您体验自由骑行的乐趣。您可以选择三种不同类型的自行车，探索一个为所有技能水平的骑行者设计的大型沙盒滑板公园。凭借有趣的物理控制，玩家可以执行特技、抓住大气，并驾驭各种挑战性地形。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274780/extras/3b75cd3e020f54d9f65a8b7afe590fb7.poster.avif?t=1772360936\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274780/extras/3b75cd3e020f54d9f65a8b7afe590fb7.webm?t=1772360936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274780/extras/3b75cd3e020f54d9f65a8b7afe590fb7.mp4?t=1772360936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >未来更新</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们计划未来的更新将带来更多功能，包括新的自定义地点、更多带有独特涂装的自行车选择和扩展的特技系统。我们希望增加不同的游戏模式，如计分时间试验和玩家与CPU对战挑战，让玩家有更多理由骑行，成为城市中最著名的骑行者！</p>",
